    "description": "Immerse yourself in a cooperative roguelike beat 'em up set in a dystopian world where humanoid animals fight for freedom! Join anarchists Tigy and Foxana in their struggle against a corporate Nazi pig dictatorship in a vast megacity farm.<br><br>With dynamic character switching and intense battles, along with vibrant graphics inspired by Western comics, this game promises nonstop action and dark humor. Perfect for fans of beat 'em ups and roguelikes looking for thrilling cooperative gameplay with friends!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cooperative Roguelike Beat 'em Up:</h2>Play with friends or solo, switching between characters at any time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Character Switching:</h2>Swap between Tigy and Foxana at any moment, adapting to challenges and enemies. Add a second player at any time to fight together.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/dde5b3ddadfcfabf9a35064258384e21.poster.avif?t=1729509708\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/dde5b3ddadfcfabf9a35064258384e21.webm?t=1729509708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/dde5b3ddadfcfabf9a35064258384e21.mp4?t=1729509708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cyberpunk Dystopian Atmosphere and Battle Against the Nazi Pig Dictatorship:</h2>Immerse yourself in the dark world of a megacity farm where humanoid animals fight for freedom and engage in an epic battle against corporate villains.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perfect for Beat 'em Up and Roguelike Fans:</h2>Designed for those seeking exhilarating and dynamic cooperative gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/7395edf0ff8bfc474c2d0b8d49621713.poster.avif?t=1729509708\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/7395edf0ff8bfc474c2d0b8d49621713.webm?t=1729509708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/7395edf0ff8bfc474c2d0b8d49621713.mp4?t=1729509708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stylish Western Comic-Inspired Graphics:</h2>Enjoy a visual style inspired by comics, creating a unique and memorable look.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dark Humor and Retrowave Vibes:</h2>Filled with humor and a vibe reminiscent of retro wave culture.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/698ba7ae5d42e476ae69e94f11ada002.poster.avif?t=1729509708\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/698ba7ae5d42e476ae69e94f11ada002.webm?t=1729509708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046310/extras/698ba7ae5d42e476ae69e94f11ada002.mp4?t=1729509708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
